https://quantumexperience.ng.bluemix.net/qx/editor

IBM Q, is an online platform available for all to get a hands on experience of experimenting with a Quantum Computer based in New York.
The online interactive GUI based tool is free and open for public for experimenting with upto 5 Qubits.

Here is a video that shows how to use it: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S52rxZG-zi0

